  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Cut your <strong>cauliflower[s]</strong> into small florets (save the stalk and leaves for later!), then add to a baking tray (or two!) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong>, a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and your <strong>ground turmeric</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for an initial 12-15 min or until the cauliflower has softened and begun to char</p>",
