      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the cauliflower is cooking, peel and slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>rice vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Mix everything together and set aside – this is your<strong> quick-pickled shallot</strong></p>",
