    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> onion wedges</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until slightly softened</p><p>Once softened, add the<strong> chopped garlic</strong> and cook for a further 1-2 min</p>",
      "order": 5,
