    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion and garlic have softened, add the <strong>drained lentils</strong> and <strong>curry powder</strong> to the pan and stir everything together</p><p>Add your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> with 80ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[100ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[130ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until thickened – these are your <strong>curried lentils</strong></p>",
